 1992   149,585,000 8,312,000                      44.6                             
 1993   173,418,000    n/a                         n/a                              
 1994   190,918,000    n/a                         n/a                              
 1995   193,349,000    n/a                         n/a                              
</PRE>
<HR>

<P>
<B>Sources:</B>  The Alan Guttmacher Institute; U.S. Bureau of
the Census; Division of Vital Statistics, National Center for
Health Statistics, Centers for Disease Control, Office of Population
Affairs, U.S. Public Health Service.
<P>
