notes that private support of the visual and performing arts reached $9.57 billion in 1993.

<LI>CPB Index in "Open to the Public," a brochure by the Corporation for Public Broadcasting, undated but referencing 
fiscal 1993.
<LI>"The Educational Power of Public Television at a Glance," Public Broadcasting Service fact sheet, February 1994.
