A Typology of Maternal Responses to Integrating Parenting and
Employment.&quot; <I>Family Relations</I> 4 [1993]: 13-20.

<p>

<li>Nancy Hellmich.  &quot;Never Enough Time for Women's Work.&quot;
<I>USA Today.</I> May 11, 1995.  4-D.

<p>

<li><I>Ibid.</I>

<p>

<li>&quot;What Mothers Want Today and Every Day&quot;, <I>op. cit.</I>

