http://www.conservative.org:80/nmp/wr-6-96.html 204.71.237.88 19970209101925 text/html 12343
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 10:20:11 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 19-Jun-96 13:27:07 GMT
