http://www.conservative.org:80/nmp/pub-1195.html 204.71.237.88 19970208200134 text/html 3789
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 20:02:20 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 15-Nov-95 22:25:03 GMT
